name: GEN2 BRUTE
description:
brute force hacks 1800 GEN2 CARDS using time as a seed
summarizing all cards found at your tez wallet address

open the #IPFS link to perform more advanced queries

query parameters:

start = start range of numeric seed
end = end range of numeric seed
fseed = text to put on the left of numeric seed
bseed = text to put on the right of numeric seed
usetime=true =use time as a seed and use start->end as a counter
maxt= do not list top stat totals above this number
maxb= do not list bottom stat totals above this number
